data.description: Welcome Home to this exceptionally maintained 4 beds, 2 full+ 2 half baths 2 Story home with a full finished basement. Updated/newer laminate wood flooring in the entry/foyer, hallway, kitchen, great room, and laundry. Kitchen has ample storage space. Island, built-in stainless appliances and a walk-in pantry opens to a massive great room. The 2nd floor opens to a large loft currently used as a home office however big enough to be another tv/media room or play room, a very spacious Owner's Suite with a coffered ceiling, ensuite bath, and large walk-in closet. 3 additional guest bedrooms each with walk-in closets completes the 2nd floor living space.
